Supreme Court — Appellate Term, June, 1900.

Before Truax, P. J., Scott and Dugro, JJ.

Jacob Meyerowitz et al., Appellants, v. Royal D. Deyo et al., Respondents Appeal from a judgment of the Municipal Court of the city of New York, borough of Manhattan. William Klingenstein, for appellants ; Pannes & Eberhardt, for respondents. Judgment affirmed, with costs.

No opinion.
